contains definition of Jenkins pipeline as a text file called Jenkinsfile

Jenkinsfile (Declarative Pipeline)
pipeline {
    agent any

    stages {
        stage('Build') {
            steps {
                echo 'Building..'
            }
        }
        stage('Test') {
            steps {
                echo 'Testing..'
            }
        }
        stage('Deploy') {
            steps {
                echo 'Deploying....'
            }
        }
    }
}

Jenkinsfile (Scripted Pipeline)
node {
    stage('Build') {
        echo 'Building....'
    }
    stage('Test') {
        echo 'Testing....'
    }
    stage('Deploy') {
        echo 'Deploying....'
    }
}
